entry.title: TISSNET 2023 Application Form (Open) Eligibility, Dates, Syllabus
entry.summary: TISSNET 2023 Admission: Tata Institute of Social Sciences is going to conduct the National Level Entrance Test (NET) for the academic year 2023.
